Package org.e2immu.support

Class Either<A,​B>

java.lang.Object
org.e2immu.support.Either<A,​B>
Type Parameters:
A -
B - 
public class Either<A,​B>
extends java.lang.Object
An object holding either an object of type A, or one of type B; it cannot hold both or neither. Either is a typical example of a E2Container without support data: final fields of an unbound parameter type, that are NotModified.
